# RoundFi CODEOWNERS
#
# Routes auto-review requests on PRs that touch specific paths. Single-
# owner skeleton for now; team usernames go here as the team expands.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <@user-or-team>
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ─── Default ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Catches anything not matched by a more specific rule below.
*                                       @alrimarleskovar

# ─── On-chain programs (protocol security) ───────────────────────────
# Highest scrutiny — any change here may require a redeploy + verify-
# build re-attestation cycle (see docs/verified-build.md).
/programs/                              @alrimarleskovar
/programs/roundfi-core/                 @alrimarleskovar
/programs/roundfi-reputation/           @alrimarleskovar
/programs/roundfi-yield-kamino/         @alrimarleskovar
/programs/roundfi-yield-mock/           @alrimarleskovar

# ─── Audit / security artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────
# Changes to disclosure policy or scope statements need explicit sign-
# off — these are the documents external auditors and bounty
# researchers anchor on.
/AUDIT_SCOPE.md                         @alrimarleskovar
/SECURITY.md                            @alrimarleskovar
/docs/security/                         @alrimarleskovar

# ─── Build / verification flow ───────────────────────────────────────
# Changes here can invalidate the on-chain OtterSec attestation PDAs
# placed for all 4 devnet programs. Review every touch.
/docs/verified-build.md                 @alrimarleskovar
/scripts/devnet/verify-*                @alrimarleskovar
/Cargo.lock                             @alrimarleskovar
/deny.toml                              @alrimarleskovar

# ─── CI / repo workflows ─────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/workflows/                     @alrimarleskovar
/.github/CODEOWNERS                     @alrimarleskovar
/.github/dependabot.yml                 @alrimarleskovar
